Package com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.documents.sequence

Provides interfaces specifying the types of sequence and alignment documents in Geneious, together with concrete classes used by sequence documents such as SequenceAnnotation and SequenceCharSequence.

Package com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.documents.sequence Description

Provides interfaces specifying the types of sequence and alignment documents in Geneious, together with concrete classes used by sequence documents such as SequenceAnnotation and SequenceCharSequence.

For default implementations of the interfaces defined in this pacakage, see the com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.implementations.sequence package.
